  <title>Choose a photo for your background</title>

  <p>You can change the background image of your desktop to make it uniquely
  yours. Choose from some of the sample photos that came on your computer, some
  of the photos you have added, or choose your favorite color.</p>

  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>Click on the <gui>User Menu</gui> on the bottom left-hand corner of
      your screen, then click on <gui>Settings</gui>.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Click on the <gui>Background</gui> button to open the panel.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Click on the <gui>Background</gui> button with the picture in it.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>There are three choices displayed on top:</p>
      <list>
        <item>
          <p>Select <gui>Wallpapers</gui> to use one of the beautiful background
          images that ship with Endless.</p>
        </item>
        <item>
          <p>Select <gui>Pictures</gui> to use one of your own photos from your
          <file>Pictures</file> folder.</p>
        </item>
        <item>
          <p>Select <gui>Colors</gui> to just use a color.</p>
        </item>
      </list>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>The settings are applied immediately.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>

